PowerShell `Get-Content` on `sshd_config` over `«ADMIN_SESSION_P1»`
.. {busc_store}
`«SSHD_CONFIG_BYTES»` from the response
.. {busc_require}
{busc_use}
`«SSHD_CONFIG_BYTES»` parses (BCG-compliant matching) to
`PubkeyAuthentication yes`, `PasswordAuthentication no`, and
