. *Phase 3 — disable powercfg sleep and hibernate*:
.. {busc_call}
`powercfg /change standby-timeout-ac 0`,
`powercfg /change standby-timeout-dc 0`, and
`powercfg /hibernate off` over `«ADMIN_SESSION_P2»`. Idempotent
.. {busc_fatal}
on `powercfg` failure with pointer to {bust_handbook_windows} — on
Modern Standby systems lacking the operator-managed
`PlatformAoAcOverride` registry write, these calls are silently
demoted to no-ops; the post-completion invigilate then surfaces the
