.. {busc_call}
{bust_invigilate_windows} for this {burp_investiture}
.. {busc_store}
`«INVIGILATE_RESULT»` from its exit status and diagnostic
.. {busc_require}
{busc_use}
`«INVIGILATE_RESULT»` is zero
